{"tid":2303011,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《APAN》年度 TOP10 人氣歌手，BTS、TWICE... 等上榜","createTime":"2020-11-27T14:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T15:56:02.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"665ed71d962a868131c9757328d06580f79b935e","tid":2303011,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T14:29:30.000Z","msg":"《2020 APAN Music Awards》公開年度 TOP10 人氣歌手，BTS、TWICE 等均上榜。<br />\n<br />\n由韓國娛樂管理協會 (Korea Entertainment Management Association，簡稱 KEMA) 主辦的《2020 APAN Music Awards》頒獎典禮，在26日公布根據粉絲投票、歌手過去一年的音源與實體銷售成績與專業評審評分而定的年度 TOP10 人氣歌手，分別是姜丹尼爾、THE BOYZ、MONSTA X、BTS 防彈少年團、SEVENTEEN、IZ*ONE、任英雄、GOT7、NCT 與 TWICE。<br />\n<br />\n此外，單純根據粉絲投票選出的全球最佳偶像是 NCT、最佳表演是姜丹尼爾、最佳 MV 是 BLACKPINK 以及最佳 All-Rounder 是 GOT7 的 JB。<br />\n<br />\n而《2020 APAN Music Awards》頒獎原訂11月28日舉辦，但受新冠肺炎 (COVID-19) 疫情影響延期。"},{"pid":"9e916d3686bf4c889f12f82d0989aa04d7be246b","tid":2303011,"uid":337986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T14:34:27.000Z","msg":"因唱歌難聽跳舞唔齊而被評為韓國top10人氣歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00052a9872301f673a9917327c511b22e36ece8","tid":2303011,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T14:34:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老母冇EXO冇RV 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5940a068c52c7720222858db6b3f3e8dbc6876","tid":2303011,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d00052a9872301f673a9917327c511b22e36ece8","tid":2303011,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T14:34:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老母冇EXO冇RV 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T14:37:51.000Z","msg":"喊出黎啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wa